Enum Class GameState

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GameState>
org.mio.progettoingsoft.GameState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<GameState>, Constable
public enum GameState extends Enum<GameState> implements Serializable
Enumerates the various states that the game can be in. These states control the flow of the game, from setup to gameplay, and define specific actions or UI presentations. The states are designed to manage the complexity of a turn-based game loop.
